# To start the game follow the steps below
1. Clone the project into your machine using terminal.
2. cd to project directory
3. Make sure you have ruby 2.7.1 version installed before to go to next step.
4. Run `bundle install` to have all the dependencies installed.
5. Run command `ruby init.rb` to start the game and follow the instructions.
6. To end the game give command `END` or press `CTRL-D`.
7. To run the test cases run `rspec`
Thank you